IMAPStore user@mail.com-remote
Host mail.autistici.org
Port 993
User user@mail.com
AuthMechs LOGIN 
SSLType IMAPS 
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore user@mail.com-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.mutt/mails/
Inbox ~/.mutt/mails/inbox

Channel user@mail.com
Master :user@mail.com-remote:
Slave :user@mail.com-local:

Create Slave 
SyncState *
Expunge Both

